name: Rabbit Delirium #1
description:
Rabbit Delirium is my 2nd collectible series, exclusive for Schizoid Bunny collectors.
If you have the entire series you will receive a special gift. If you have 15 or more editions of Schizoid Bunny in your collection, you will receive this Rabbit Delirium #1, until I have only 1 left.
If you are an anonymous collector and agree to have me send it to you, please contact me in some way to let me know.
